      <div class="project-description">
        <p class="p-project">
          Race Hopper is a 3D platform video game built with the WebGL API designed to be played in the web browser.
          Players must hop over obstacles to advance to the next level. Jewels may be collected to obtain a better
          score. This game was created solo in 2 days for a hack-a-thon.
        </p>
        <p class="p-project p-tech">
          Technologies: C#, Unity, WebGL
        </p>
      </div>

